<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Cancel Account Deletion – Verification Code</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px;">
    <h2 style="color: #1a1a1a;">Verify your identity to cancel deletion</h2>
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>
      We received a request to cancel the scheduled deletion of your Examforge account.
      Use the code below to confirm it's really you. This code expires in <strong>10 minutes</strong>.
    </p>
    <div style="background: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; text-align: center; margin: 24px 0;">
      <span style="font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #1a1a1a;">{{otp}}</span>
    </div>
    <p>
      If you did not attempt to cancel your account deletion, you can safely ignore this email —
      your account will continue on its scheduled deletion timeline.
    </p>
    <p style="color: #888; font-size: 13px;">— The Examforge Team</p>
  </body>
</html>
